edu.neu.ccs.cs5004.problem1.substitute

Class abstractSubstituteTeacher

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.ccs.cs5004.problem1.substitute.abstractSubstituteTeacher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITeacher
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    substituteTeacher

    public abstract class abstractSubstituteTeacher
extends Object
implements ITeacher
    An abstract class representing a Substitute Teacher. The substitute teacher does not have any track of students so this abstract class helps reduce repeat code.
